# UART RX Test Program for RV32I
# 1. Write 0x2 to 0x4000C (RX enable bit)  
# 2. Loop: read 0x4000C, if bit 0 is 0 then continue loop (wait for data)
# 3. Read received data from 0x40008 (UART RX data address)

